{"tid":2179191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：解雇反共公務員是因了解而分手","createTime":"2020-08-29T02:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T04:54:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4f82a7b30053bee3193344181f444934574dd093","tid":2179191,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"聶德權：終止被起訴公務員試用期前會有申訴機會 <br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局長聶德權表示，若有新入職公務員因非法公眾活動被捕及起訴，部門首長在考慮是否終止涉事公務員試用期時，會為當事人提供申訴機會，確保做法公平、公正。他在一個電台節目形容，在有關安排下，涉事公務員與政府是<span class=\"gold\">「因誤會而結合，因了解而分手」</span>，在3年試用期內，政府了解到員工是否合適人選，僱員亦了解職位是否適合自己，強調政府對公務員品行、操守及表現有嚴格要求。 <br />\n<br />\n聶德權又在本台節目表示，現時仍有部分新型冠狀病毒確診個案感染源頭不明，最重要是減少人流及嚴控社交距離，因此各部門仍未全面恢復運作，但已因應情況，恢復基本服務，並繼續維持緊急服務。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2354773&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a4282602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354773</a>"},{"pid":"8d88b397a2390c8742c8500028003bdca81ca993","tid":2179191,"uid":150902,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:08:45.000Z","msg":"極像了愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b089bca36ae3d4e3105679106bab9cde4028aa2d","tid":2179191,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:12:25.000Z","msg":"佢係咪沉完支共勾引佢隻雞"},{"pid":"2ccd6771a775a8fcd6e63cf4068e1a27ae9e81e4","tid":2179191,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩比喻黎"},{"pid":"48853e26010cc39750cab68477f6e0ad26f49507","tid":2179191,"uid":21028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"冇文化拎個比